  "description": "<b>消息人士周一透露，微软正筹备下调面向小屏幕平板电脑的Windows操作系统售价，在移动计算市场进行竞争寻求优势。</b>消息人士称，微软做出产品价格调整，旨在让更多的制造商在平板电脑中采用Windows RT操作系统。Windows RT是微软面向ARM架构的平板电脑的一款操作系统。据悉，此次价格调整主要针对的是小屏幕平板电脑。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2cc4c12c/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239723.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%AA%81%E5%9B%B4%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8+%E6%88%96%E4%B8%8B%E8%B0%83Windows+RT%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%94%AE%E4%BB%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239723.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%AA%81%E5%9B%B4%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8+%E6%88%96%E4%B8%8B%E8%B0%83Windows+RT%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%94%AE%E4%BB%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239723.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%AA%81%E5%9B%B4%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8+%E6%88%96%E4%B8%8B%E8%B0%83Windows+RT%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%94%AE%E4%BB%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239723.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%AA%81%E5%9B%B4%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8+%E6%88%96%E4%B8%8B%E8%B0%83Windows+RT%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%94%AE%E4%BB%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239723.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%AA%81%E5%9B%B4%E7%A7%BB